%% PROPOSED: FRACAS Record Lifecycle
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Reported
    Reported --> Classified
    Classified --> Contained
    Contained --> Under_Investigation
    Under_Investigation --> CA_Defined
    CA_Defined --> Action_Type

    state Action_Type <<choice>>

    Action_Type --> ECO_Path: Design change
    Action_Type --> Procedure_Path: Procedure update
    Action_Type --> Risk_Accepted: Accept risk
    ECO_Path --> Implementing
    Procedure_Path --> Implementing
    Risk_Accepted --> Verified
    Implementing --> Verified
    Verified --> Effectiveness_Review: Pass
    Verified --> Under_Investigation: Rework needed
    Effectiveness_Review --> Closed: Effective
    Effectiveness_Review --> Under_Investigation: Recurrence
    Closed --> [*]
